811
01:49:49,781 --> 01:49:55,620
<i>Depois do teu adeus</i>

812
01:49:56,204 --> 01:50:02,711
<i>Senti toda a minha dor</i>

813
01:50:03,128 --> 01:50:06,965
<i>Só e chorando</i>

814
01:50:07,508 --> 01:50:10,469
<i>Chorando</i>

815
01:50:10,886 --> 01:50:14,223
<i>Chorando</i>

816
